<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.1.10">
<l>cenne lārvayal cūḻtiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>maṉṉu nāraṇaṉ nampi piṟantamai</l>
<l>miṉṉu nūlviṭṭu cittaṉ virittavip</l>
<l>paṉṉu pāṭalval lārkkillai pāvamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is no evil for those who master this song of praise</l>
<l>that was expounded [by] Viṣṇu Cittaṉ [with] the shining text</l>
<l>[about] the birth of the eternal Lord Nāraṇaṉ [in] Tirukkōṭṭiyūr,</l>
<l>surrounded by abundant agricultural tracts of superior paddy.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
